# Project 2
Three-Tier Web App with Kubernetes

Core Objectives
- Get hands-on kubernetes experience
- Understand how microservices work

Tech Stack
UI Layer  - React.js
Backend  - Node.js for the APIs
Database - MongoDB, a NoSQL database
DevOps Tools - Docker, Kubernetes

Steps
- Build Docker images for tiers
- Write kubernetes manifest files
- Run deployments to create Pods

- Expose Pods using services
- Check microservice connection

Potential Problems
- Beginners often get confused between Pods and containers
"CrashLoopBackOff" errors or memory kills might happen if you haven't configured
the correct ports for the services to communicate

Time Investments
6-8 hourse for beginners

